create
===
type (single/combo, required)
platform (select from existing platforms, required)
profit % (required)
add products -> dynamic add/remove product rows, each row will have product (select from existing products under selected platform), quantity, price (auto filled from product price but editable)

ar nicher dike etar total calculate hobe dynamically -> subtotal , profit amount, total with profit, expected income (sub total er sathe profit er calculate kore dekhabe real time e)

